== Azur Lane Wiki Templates ==
This is a list of commonly used templates on this wiki. Please expand this section with more examples.

=== ShipDisplay ===
Used to display ship information.
<pre><nowiki>
{{ShipDisplay
|ship=Enterprise
|id=077
|rarity=Super Rare
|type=Aircraft Carrier
|faction=Eagle Union
|class=Yorktown
|artist=
|va=
|obtain=
|construct=
}}
</nowiki></pre>

=== Furniture ===
Used to display furniture information.
<pre><nowiki>
{{Furniture
|name=
|image=
|description=
|rarity=
|type=
|obtain=
}}
</nowiki></pre>

=== IconHover ===
Used to create an icon that displays a tooltip on hover.
<pre><nowiki>
{{IconHover|item=TBF Avenger (VT-8)|text=TBF Avenger (VT-8)}}
</nowiki></pre>

=== Display ===
A versatile template for displaying items, equipment, and more.
<pre><nowiki>
{{Display|item=Cognitive Chips|count=1000}}
</nowiki></pre>

=== EventShopItem ===
Used for displaying items in an event shop.
<pre><nowiki>
{{EventShopItem
|item=
|cost=
|amount=
|pool=
}}
</nowiki></pre>

